IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
PROGRAM-ID. IMAGE-IO-TEST.
INPUT-OUTPUT SECTION.
FILE-CONTROL.
    SELECT IMG-COMBINED ASSIGN TO "GPU-IMAGE-0-0" 
        ORGANIZATION IS IMAGE-2D.
    SELECT TEX-ONLY ASSIGN TO "GPU-IMAGE-0-1" 
        ORGANIZATION IS TEXTURE-2D.
    SELECT SMP-ONLY ASSIGN TO "GPU-SAMPLER-0-2" 
        ORGANIZATION IS SAMPLER.
    SELECT STO-IMAGE ASSIGN TO "GPU-IMAGE-0-3" 
        ORGANIZATION IS STORAGE-2D.
DATA DIVISION.
FILE SECTION.
FD  IMG-COMBINED.
01  REC-C PIC V(4).
FD  TEX-ONLY.
01  REC-T PIC V(4).
FD  STO-IMAGE.
    FORMAT IS RGBA32F.
01  REC-S PIC V(4).
WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.
01  UV-COORD PIC V(2) VALUE (0.5, 0.5).
01  PIXEL-VAL PIC V(4).
PROCEDURE DIVISION.
    MAIN.
        READ IMG-COMBINED AT UV-COORD INTO PIXEL-VAL.
        READ TEX-ONLY WITH SMP-ONLY AT UV-COORD INTO PIXEL-VAL.
        READ STO-IMAGE AT UV-COORD INTO PIXEL-VAL.
        WRITE STO-IMAGE FROM PIXEL-VAL AT UV-COORD.
        GOBACK.
